{"tid":2409774,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"窮人同有錢人炒股上的差異","createTime":"2021-02-16T05:40:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-16T08:02:48.000Z","uid":15636,"like":16,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"a2da7ae853a3d623db5bc5bf1a13a7d92c92dd98","tid":2409774,"uid":15636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:40:28.000Z","msg":"富人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />同窮人<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />上年股JOY後各拎咗100萬同100萬出黎炒股買TSLA<br />\n利申返先：呢到既窮富並唔係單純指金錢上，而係大家所謂既「窮人思想」<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">半個月升咗一倍後，TSLA翻咗一倍</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：哇，好有力喎TSLA，慢慢坐先<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：哇，好有力喎TSLA，但升咗成倍咁多，等佢回調我再入賺盡佢先<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">又過咗成個月，TSLA回調咗20%左後再爆升兩倍</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：哇，牛市呀，好有力喎TSLA，繼續慢慢坐先<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：正，又升咗成倍，出出入人又賺多咗幾十萬，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />你都賣啦依家高位<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">又過咗幾個月TSLA升多咗幾倍</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：哇，個市好撚牛呀，繼好有力喎TSLA，繼續慢慢坐先<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />：正，出出入入，賺到笑，少年股神就係我<br />\n但事實上，大家賺既錢都差唔多。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">咁大家都知TSLA繼續爆升，又拆股，一年升成十倍有多</span><br />\n最後：<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />晚晚炒美股，返工都無精神，好彩鐵飯碗無比人炒。去到拆股個排回調又無入到，望住TSLA升升升，當然繼續係到出出入入啦，有賺有蝕，最有都由100萬賺到300。可惜最後受連登仔影響，拎咗一球野去玩GME，輸晒咁制<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/smile2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />返工放工進修學習，開市睇一睇校好止蝕就訓覺，最後仲轉公司加人工，到依家都持有TSLA中，由100萬揸到上1000萬。聽到人地講GME，AMC，不禁冷笑一下。繼續做TSLA股東，打算尋找另一間有潛力公司長期持有。"},{"pid":"5b2a8660ceebdeeb7645f0355dad92921a41d1ad","tid":2409774,"uid":184509,"like":2,"dislike":19,"score":-17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:41:05.000Z","msg":"窮人那有100m?😥"},{"pid":"a0fe21d047c4d02b3c104d369aa421a1027d58fc","tid":2409774,"uid":15636,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"5b2a8660ceebdeeb7645f0355dad92921a41d1ad","tid":2409774,"uid":184509,"like":2,"dislike":19,"score":-17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:41:05.000Z","msg":"窮人那有100m?😥"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:41:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>利申返先：呢到既窮富並唔係單純指金錢上，而係大家所謂既「窮人思想」</blockquote>"},{"pid":"d8c731fc6b77a859553d47d655523e05dff2a90a","tid":2409774,"uid":79756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:42:47.000Z","msg":"老實講句。有錢人個投資組合起碼50%買基金，甚至更加多"},{"pid":"8beb89131ca084945aec7f1bdfbfb3bdff934a2d","tid":2409774,"uid":15636,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8c731fc6b77a859553d47d655523e05dff2a90a","tid":2409774,"uid":79756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:42:47.000Z","msg":"老實講句。有錢人個投資組合起碼50%買基金，甚至更加多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:44:32.000Z","msg":"呢到既窮富並唔係單純指金錢上，而係大家所謂既「窮人思想」"},{"pid":"bae66bcd204d10e5dbdc47ce224756739a0b6b1f","tid":2409774,"uid":40309,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"d8c731fc6b77a859553d47d655523e05dff2a90a","tid":2409774,"uid":79756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:42:47.000Z","msg":"老實講句。有錢人個投資組合起碼50%買基金，甚至更加多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:45:07.000Z","msg":"有返幾千萬郁小小等於 人地all in 洗鬼搏<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d996258d89e41861d76cdfd749a6283f0c5612c7","tid":2409774,"uid":28558,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:45:58.000Z","msg":"樓主都幾無聊"},{"pid":"fc0d8055c7501f1162ba7c44594702b8cc70744e","tid":2409774,"uid":190928,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score"