話傻仔 <br />\n宜家800幾蚊 又話馬後炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0371bdcab231346b02e84bbc3641dcd58e150df8","tid":2409774,"uid":377234,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d8c731fc6b77a859553d47d655523e05dff2a90a","tid":2409774,"uid":79756,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:42:47.000Z","msg":"老實講句。有錢人個投資組合起碼50%買基金，甚至更加多"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T06:52:56.000Z","msg":"咪就係"},{"pid":"5bd035387b1f78adc05ed5e73eb0eeab5b53d8ec","tid":2409774,"uid":149844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T07:39:49.000Z","msg":"高操作又成功賺得多過長坐<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"659f2b20e919fee4c44522dd8bceb1edd7184e79","tid":2409774,"uid":97314,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"d996258d89e41861d76cdfd749a6283f0c5612c7","tid":2409774,"uid":28558,"like":10,"dislike":1,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:45:58.000Z","msg":"樓主都幾無聊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T07:43:06.000Z","msg":"窮人先會用咁多時間响連登打咁大段故仔"},{"pid":"66b34b4f925c493cb1cfebf0630107dc11527363","tid":2409774,"uid":133183,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5b2a8660ceebdeeb7645f0355dad92921a41d1ad","tid":2409774,"uid":184509,"like":2,"dislike":19,"score":-17,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T05:41:05.000Z","msg":"窮人那有100m?😥"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T07:50:32.000Z","msg":"1m=100萬<br />\n100m係一億"},{"pid":"caea4760d2e17a9b91295288661e338109143593","tid":2409774,"uid":113356,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T07:54:54.000Z","msg":"富人既100萬佔佢身家好小，點坐都無所謂，窮人既100萬係身家既7or8成，炒波幅，都係個句啦，有技術自然會跑贏，無技術就可以講88"},{"pid":"9a6c791ca17e6e7ee3c9043793f7250b6785a0b8","tid":2409774,"uid":70888,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T08:00:39.000Z","msg":"愈多人玩短炒就愈好<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我睇住依班人就好似睇生態紀錄片咁，成班水牛過河比大鱷慢慢食<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />每日都上演<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />精彩<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大半年前我就一早買晒貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />連mpf都買晒北美<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n得閒高位放少少，好多股已經負成本<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一個月都係trade幾次<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />食得好瞓得好<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n大家記住繼續好似GME咁炒就啱，代表個市好健康<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n當全世界買Tesla arkk tsm我就驚了<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/arrogant.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3f2ffa16a8377a8d5f5fbaaa0b89fb1f68a3cbdc","tid":2409774,"uid":162959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-16T08:02:48.000Z","msg":"富人都要返工咁慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}